-->Streamlit is an open-source Python framework used to build interactive 
web applications directly from Python scripts, 
without writing HTML, CSS, or JavaScript.

-->googletrans is a Python library that provides an unofficial 
interface to Google Translate, allowing developers to translate 
text between multiple languages using Python.

-->Translator is a class inside the googletrans library that performs the actual translation.

-->gTTS (Google Text-to-Speech) is a Python library that 
